HEADWORD: Accused
<hw>Ac*cused"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Charged with
offense; <as>as, an <ex>accused</ex> person</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>Commonly used substantively; as, the <xex>accused</xex>, one
